<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-1a' );" name="000-1a" class="pb">[000-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:196'>欽定四庫全書　　　　經部四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='196:220'>　㤗泉鄉禮　　　　　　禮類六<span class='krp-note'>雜禮書之屬/</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='220:226'>　　提要</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='226:253'>　　　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>等謹按泰泉鄉禮七卷明黄佐撰佐有樂典已</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='253:277'>　　　著録其學恪守程朱嘗與王守仁論知行合一之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='277:301'>　　　　㫖數相辨難守仁亦稱其直諒然不以聚徒講</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='301:325'>　　　　學名故翛然於門户外焉是書乃其以廣西提</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='325:349'>　　　　　學僉事乞休家居時所著凡六卷首舉鄉禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='349:375'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-1b' );" name="000-1b" class="pb">[000-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='375:398'>　　　　綱領以立教明倫敬身為主次則冠婚以下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='398:421'>　　　　四禮皆略為條教第取其今世可行而又不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='421:444'>　　　　倍戾於古者次舉五事曰鄉約鄉校社倉鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='444:467'>　　　　社保甲皆深寓端本厚俗之意末以士相見</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='467:490'>　　　　禮及投壺鄉社禮别為一卷附之大抵皆簡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='490:513'>　　　　明切要可見施行在明人著述中猶為有用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='513:536'>　　　　之書視所補註之皇極經世支離曼衍敝精</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='536:559'>　　　　神於無用之地者有空言實事之分矣乾隆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='559:585'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-2a' );" name="000-2a" class="pb">[000-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='585:600'>　　　　四十二年十月恭校上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='600:633'>　　　　　　　　總纂官<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>紀昀<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>陸錫熊<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>孫士毅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='633:660'>　　　　　　　　　　　總　校　官　<span class='krp-note'>臣/</span>　陸費墀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='680:706'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-3a' );" name="000-3a" class="pb">[000-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='706:714'>泰泉鄉禮原序</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='714:737'>夫道有隆汙俗由升降故俗者其効情者乎情者其効</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='737:760'>治者乎故曰人情者聖王之田也故禮以耕之義以種</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='760:783'>之學以耨之仁以聚之樂以安之故治隆而俗不庬也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='783:806'>周秦之際其宇宙之大限乎徳色誶語賈生有遺戚矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='806:829'>間有興禮讓修教化於郡縣之中民亦翕然丕變其俗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='829:852'>孟子曰乃若其情則可以為善矣斯非其明徵哉吾廣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='852:875'>宫詹學士泰泉黄公咨嗟薄俗嘅然逖慕於古之遺治</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='875:901'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-3b' );" name="000-3b" class="pb">[000-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='901:924'>昔在家食輯為鄉禮一書要在於敬身明倫講信修睦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='924:947'>主鄉約以勵規勸而謹鄉校設社倉則豫教與養秩里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='947:970'>社聫保甲則重祀與戎身心既淑禮樂備舉凡以約其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='970:993'>情而治之使鄉之人習而行焉善俗其有㡬乎此公之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='993:1016'>志也是故約正以綱之教讀以紀之士大夫以帥之有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1016:1039'>司以表正而董治之斯所謂待人而行者乎香山令文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1039:1062'>岩鄧君見而嘆曰韙哉興化善治之道其必由此歟夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1062:1085'>情比扵禮而鄉治矣俗成扵鄉而天下治矣不帥胡化</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1085:1111'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-4a' );" name="000-4a" class="pb">[000-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1111:1134'>不令胡從我其責哉則造扵公而請焉曰之邑也公之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1134:1157'>鄉也公實帥之予小子匪表正之能敢不黽勉以承公</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1157:1180'>後矧曰嗣必有興者乎既乃序其書而梓之葢廣徳心</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1180:1203'>而公諸天下也謂何子鮤盍申識之鮤鄙人也何敢為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1203:1226'>佞然實幸其相與以有成且將以風乎治政者也夫古</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1226:1249'>今人豈不相及哉君必勉之乃若普惠養之政息兼并</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1249:1272'>之風使其富而可敎從之也輕則有孔孟之矩在君必</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1272:1295'>能與天下之英熟圖之矣書曰邇可逺在兹其斯編之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1295:1321'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-4b' );" name="000-4b" class="pb">[000-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1321:1339'>謂與嘉靖己酉夏四月既望順徳何鮤撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1339:1362'>詹事泰泉公先提督廣西學政所著鄉禮凡六卷兹又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1362:1385'>以士相見禮及投壺鄉射諸篇附之合七卷云先是書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1385:1408'>葢刻扵廣之藩司頒諸郡邑行矣彼都人士講明誦説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1408:1431'>見諸行事夫固有所感發興起以蹈道遷義哉香山内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1431:1454'>周邑井外接島夷四顧汪洋迥千里而孤懸海表焉其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1454:1477'>士民錯居阻險思奢儉之中厪耕織之務能知其所為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1477:1500'>已葢自昔為然若乃親親尊尊之制比閭族黨之交律</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1500:1526'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-5a' );" name="000-5a" class="pb">[000-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1526:1549'>已教人之法周旋升降之文鐘鼓管絃之聲凡以反亷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1549:1572'>愧之節仁義之厚使人人回心向道日遷善逺罪而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1572:1595'>自知顧在此而不在彼也夫民剛柔輕重遲速異齊繋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1595:1618'>水土之風氣故謂之風動静取舍唯上所好惡故謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1618:1641'>俗風俗淳厚風雨時節災害不生凡民知所自愛重犯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1641:1664'>法亡盜賊就地險逺和氣之應賢扵内郡斯所謂禮教</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1664:1687'>素行政修民和之所致哉書曰光天之下至于海隅此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1687:1710'>言王者文命所敷無逺不届也在昔文王之徳其下化</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1710:1736'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-5b' );" name="000-5b" class="pb">[000-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1736:1759'>之周南召南之詩作焉故論風俗茂美于周為盛聖天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1759:1782'>子端拱穆清化行海外則斯邑諸人士其扵禮樂教化</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1782:1805'>政俗雍容之會亦維風可觀矣夫以文王之徳詩人繫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1805:1828'>之扵二南斯豈非周召之治哉今公以鄉禮名書行且</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1828:1851'>達之天下而上致其君興太平成雅俗書曰始于家邦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1851:1874'>終于四海斯大臣輔相之事公以為何如遷不佞敬取</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1874:1897'>是書重刻于香山之邑齋夫香山公桑梓在焉公用之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1897:1920'>於天下其次第則自斯始嘉靖己酉春二月之吉知香</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1920:1946'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0090', 'WYG', '000-6a' );" name="000-6a" class="pb">[000-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1946:1955'>山縣事閩鄧遷叙</span><br/>
</p>
